     (para "
While a non-zero buffer object is bound to the "
           (code "GL_PIXEL_PACK_BUFFER")
           " target, 
            the following commands are affected: "
           (code "glGetCompressedTexImage")
           ", "
           (code "glGetConvolutionFilter")
           ", "
           (code "glGetHistogram")
           ", "
           (code "glGetMinmax")
           ", "
           (code "glGetPixelMap")
           ", "
           (code "glGetPolygonStipple")
